│   // Variables for our state machines.                                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                                                             │
│   // FirstTrueElement/SecondTrueElement - Used to emit a comparison of the form                                                                                             │
│   // "i == 47 | i == 87", where 47 is the first index the condition is true for,                                                                                            │
